<style>
  .service-chat-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) 360px;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .service-chat-card,
  .service-chat-side {
    border: 1px solid rgba(37, 35, 33, 0.08);
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(34, 34, 34, 0.05);
  }

  .service-chat-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto minmax(420px, 1fr) auto;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .service-chat-header,
  .service-chat-product,
  .service-chat-composer,
  .service-chat-side {
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .service-chat-header,
  .service-chat-product {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(37, 35, 33, 0.08);
  }

  .service-chat-action-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .service-chat-action-row a,
  .service-chat-action-row form,
  .service-chat-action-row button {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .service-chat-reserved-note {
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: rgba(37, 35, 33, 0.06);
    color: rgba(37, 35, 33, 0.66);
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .service-chat-messages {
    padding: 18px 20px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    max-height: 62vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.36), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6));
  }

  .service-message-group {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .service-message-time {
    justify-self: center;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(37, 35, 33, 0.08);
    color: rgba(37, 35, 33, 0.58);
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .service-message-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  .service-message-row.mine {
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .service-message-avatar {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: #ffe351;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .service-message-row.mine .service-message-avatar {
    background: #252321;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .service-message-bubble {
    max-width: min(78%, 640px);
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-radius: 18px 18px 18px 8px;
    background: #fff7db;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(34, 34, 34, 0.05);
  }

  .service-message-row.mine .service-message-bubble {
    border-radius: 18px 18px 8px 18px;
    background: #252321;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .service-message-meta {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(37, 35, 33, 0.56);
  }

  .service-message-row.mine .service-message-meta {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  .service-message-image {
    display: block;
    max-width: min(280px, 48vw);
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  .service-chat-composer textarea {
    min-height: 110px;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .service-side-meta {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .service-side-block {
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: #fffdf7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .service-chat-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .service-identity-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-left: 10px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9, #f1f8e9);
    border: 1px solid #a5d6a7;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .service-identity-icon {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .service-identity-name {
    color: #2e7d32;
  }

  .service-identity-badge {
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #4caf50;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .service-message-row.service-sender .service-message-avatar {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4caf50, #2e7d32);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .service-message-row.service-sender .service-message-bubble {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9, #f1f8e9);
    border: 1px solid #a5d6a7;
  }

  .service-message-row.service-sender .service-message-meta {
    color: #2e7d32;
  }
</style>

<div class="mb-4">
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start flex-wrap gap-3 mb-3">
    <div>
      <h2 class="h4 mb-1"><%= conversation.listing_title %></h2>
      <div class="text-muted small">
        <%= conversation.listing_type === "wanted" ? "求购帖" : "出售帖" %>
        路
        <%= conversation.district_name %>
        路
        最后活跃 <%= new Date(conversation.last_active_at || Date.now()).toLocaleString("zh-CN") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-outline-dark rounded-4" href="/service/dashboard">返回列表</a>
  </div>
  <div class="service-chat-action-row" style="padding: 12px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(37,35,33,0.08);">
    <span class="text-muted small me-2">独立对话:</span>
    <a class="btn rounded-4" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8f5e9,#f1f8e9);border:1px solid #a5d6a7;color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;" href="/service/conversations/<%= conversation.route_id %>/chat?type=buyer">🛡️ 与买家私聊</a>
    <a class="btn rounded-4" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8f5e9,#f1f8e9);border:1px solid #a5d6a7;color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;" href="/service/conversations/<%= conversation.route_id %>/chat?type=seller">🛡️ 与卖家私聊</a>
    <div style="width: 1px; height: 24px; background: rgba(37,35,33,0.15); margin: 0 5px;"></div>
    <form method="POST" action="/service/conversations/<%= conversation.route_id %>/processed" style="margin: 0;">
      <input type="hidden" name="back_to" value="detail" />
      <button class="btn <%= conversation.is_processed ? 'btn-outline-secondary' : 'btn-success' %> rounded-4" type="submit">
        <%= conversation.is_processed ? "恢复处理中" : "标记已处理" %>
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="service-chat-layout">
  <section class="service-chat-card">
    <header class="service-chat-header d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
      <div>
        <div class="fw-semibold">
          客服对话
          <span class="service-identity-tag">
            <span class="service-identity-icon">🛡️</span>
            <span class="service-identity-name"><%= currentServiceUser.nickname || "客服" %></span>
            <span class="service-identity-badge">官方客服</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="small text-muted">
          买家：<%= conversation.buyer_name %>
          路
          卖家：<%= conversation.seller_name %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="status-pill <%= conversation.is_processed ? 'closed' : 'processing' %>">
        <%= conversation.is_processed ? "已处理" : "处理中" %>
      </span>
    </header>

    <section class="service-chat-product d-grid gap-3">
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
        <% if (conversation.listing_image) { %>
          <img src="<%= conversation.listing_image %>" alt="" style="width:84px;height:84px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:18px;" />
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="rounded-4 bg-light d-grid place-items-center" style="width:84px;height:84px;">无图</div>
        <% } %>
        <div>
          <div class="fw-semibold"><%= conversation.listing_title %></div>
          <div class="text-muted small mb-1"><%= conversation.district_name %></div>
          <div class="h5 mb-0">￥<%= Number(conversation.listing_price || 0).toFixed(2) %></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-chat-reserved-note">
        “退款”和“不批准”按钮已经预留路由，当前点击会先记录动作并提示成功，后续我们可以直接接入真实接口。
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-chat-messages" id="service-chat-messages">
      <% if (!messages.length) { %>
        <div class="text-center text-muted py-5">当前还没有消息，客服可以先发一条问候。</div>
      <% } %>

      <% messages.forEach((message) => { %>
        <div class="service-message-group">
          <div class="service-message-time"><%= new Date(message.created_at || Date.now()).toLocaleString("zh-CN") %></div>
          <div class="service-message-row <%= message.is_service_sender ? 'mine' : '' %> <%= message.is_service_sender ? 'service-sender' : '' %>">
            <% if (!message.is_service_sender) { %>
              <div class="service-message-avatar"><%= String(message.sender_name || "?").slice(0, 2) %></div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="service-message-bubble">
              <div class="service-message-meta">
                <%= message.sender_name %>
                <% if (message.is_service_sender) { %>
                  <span class="service-identity-badge" style="margin-left:4px;">客服</span>
                <% } %>
              </div>
              <% if (message.is_image && message.image_url) { %>
                <a href="<%= message.image_url %>" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                  <img class="service-message-image" src="<%= message.image_url %>" alt="聊天图片" />
                </a>
              <% } else { %>
                <div><%= message.content || "（空消息）" %></div>
              <% } %>
            </div>

            <% if (message.is_service_sender) { %>
              <div class="service-message-avatar"><%= String(currentServiceUser.nickname || "客服").slice(0, 2) %></div>
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% }) %>
    </section>

    <footer class="service-chat-composer">
      <form method="POST" action="/service/conversations/<%= conversation.route_id %>/messages" class="d-grid gap-3">
        <label for="service-reply" class="form-label fw-semibold mb-0">客服回复</label>
        <textarea
          id="service-reply"
          name="content"
          class="form-control rounded-4"
          placeholder="输入要发送给买家 / 卖家的消息..."
          required
        ></textarea>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <div class="text-muted small">当前回复会直接进入这笔交易对话，用户端会在原聊天窗口看到。</div>
          <button class="btn btn-dark rounded-4 px-4" type="submit">发送回复</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </footer>
  </section>

  <aside class="service-chat-side">
    <div class="service-side-meta">
      <div class="service-side-block">
        <div class="fw-semibold mb-2">对话信息</div>
        <div class="small text-muted">会话 ID</div>
        <div class="mb-2"><%= conversation.id %></div>
        <div class="small text-muted">当前状态</div>
        <div><%= conversation.is_processed ? "已处理" : "处理中" %></div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-side-block">
        <div class="fw-semibold mb-2">买卖双方</div>
        <div class="mb-2">买家：<%= conversation.buyer_name %></div>
        <div class="text-muted small mb-3"><%= conversation.buyer_openid %></div>
        <div class="mb-2">卖家：<%= conversation.seller_name %></div>
        <div class="text-muted small"><%= conversation.seller_openid %></div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-side-block">
        <div class="fw-semibold mb-2">预留动作</div>
        <div class="small text-muted mb-3">
          如果你现在只想先把流程入口摆出来，就先用这两个按钮；等你要接真实退款或不批准逻辑时，我们直接复用这两个路由。
        </div>
        <div class="service-chat-action-row">
          <form method="POST" action="/service/conversations/<%= conversation.route_id %>/refund">
            <input type="hidden" name="back_to" value="detail" />
            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary rounded-4" type="submit">退款（预留）</button>
          </form>
          <form method="POST" action="/service/conversations/<%= conversation.route_id %>/reject">
            <input type="hidden" name="back_to" value="detail" />
            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger rounded-4" type="submit">不批准（预留）</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-side-block">
        <div class="fw-semibold mb-2">客服提示</div>
        <div class="small text-muted">
          可先确认区县、成色、面交方式，再引导双方留在站内沟通。
          如问题已解决，记得点击“标记已处理”。
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>

<script>
  (function () {
    const panel = document.getElementById("service-chat-messages");
    if (panel) {
      panel.scrollTop = panel.scrollHeight;
    }
  })();
</script>
